<i>noun</i>: 사마귀 [사ː마귀], 물사마귀 [물사마귀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>사마귀 [사ː마귀]</dt><br>
<dd>wart</dd><br>
<dd>피부 위에 쌀알만 하게 돋은 납작한 군살.</dd><br>
<dd>A small lump that grows on the skin, being about the size of a grain of rice.</dd><br>
<dt>물사마귀 [물사마귀]</dt><br>
<dd>wart</dd><br>
<dd>피부에 밥알만 한 크기로 불룩하게 생긴 군살.</dd><br>
<dd>Thickened skin growth roughly the size of a grain of rice.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>